{"tid":2506327,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"5人被控理大串謀參與暴動 次被告早前高院批准保釋 其餘4名被告今於區院全部保釋申請獲批!","createTime":"2021-04-27T08:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T19:00:08.000Z","uid":240362,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d5b1778b1846e3a02913bc8d56a3bc96d169f19e","tid":2506327,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T08:44:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15293&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oAz7jHi%2Fw8vyA5J9XtqU0Cw%3D&h=d2949e69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15293</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院第廿七庭 <br />\n#高勁修首席區域法院法官 #聆取對控罪的回答 #1111理大 #理大事件<br />\n<br />\nA1:林(22)🛑還押至今約50日<br />\nA2:姜(22) 曾還押一個月<br />\nA3:姜(21)🛑還押至今約50日<br />\nA4:陳(23)🛑還押至今約50日<br />\nA5:陳(22)🛑還押至今約50日<br />\n<br />\n控罪：串謀參與暴動<br />\n<br />\n案情：<br />\n5人被控或約於2019年11月11日與或約於2019年11月14日，首尾兩日包括在內，在香港一同串謀與其他不知名人士於香港理工大學參與暴動。<br />\n========================<br />\n<br />\n1629各被告保釋申請陳詞已完，主控已回應，現由辯方再回應<br />\n<br />\n1634已回應完，靜晒<br />\n1636等緊結果，聽到大家呼吸聲<br />\n1640仲等緊<br />\n1643全部保釋申請獲批‼️"},{"pid":"f7689bc7aeed0edbab1a00c8ae6247375a57fb0c","tid":2506327,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T08:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fff3226ed3fc648e71a323827511b014adaa435","tid":2506327,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T08:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=