A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210427%2FPR7D7MBFBBEGBELCNTIAUS6PNA%2F&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oAz7jHi%2Fw8vyA5J9XtqU0Cw%3D&h=8491efce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210427%2FPR7D7MBFBBEGBELCNTIAUS6PNA%2F&h=ca81581d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210427/PR7D7MBFBBEGBELCNTIAUS6PNA/</a>"},{"pid":"6b146a2d4af4ad005997b2d98e5d157337d193bb","tid":2506327,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T14:09:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3e5e560d378530462e12a38423b02f0b6dfc1f","tid":2506327,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T14:15:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7442379011497fb9dc1cabe6bc01892506a83d41","tid":2506327,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac3e5e560d378530462e12a38423b02f0b6dfc1f","tid":2506327,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T14:15:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T18:55:40.000Z","msg":"2019 年 11 月理大爆發嚴重警民衝突， 5 名案發時為理大學生的男女上月被警方拘捕，被控在校園串謀暴動，案件今（27 日）在區域法院再訊。除了次被告早前向高院申請保釋獲批，餘下被告還押個半月後，終獲准以 10 萬元現金保釋，另須遵守宵禁等條件。法官高勁修指，三名被告即將考試，法庭可用保釋條件平衡潛逃風險；第五被告雖不是學生，但考慮其個人情況，亦可獲保釋。有被告親友聞獲釋消息，不禁痛哭。<br />\n<br />\n法官高勁修聽畢辯方陳詞，批准四人保釋申請。他表示案件非常嚴重，亦不是沒有證據，明白控方「好著緊」，不希望被告潛逃，表示理解控方關注。<br />\n<br />\n不過，他指案中三名被告都是大學四年級學生，即將面對考試，認為法庭可用保釋條件平衡潛逃風險。至於第五被告，法官指他現在不是學生，但考慮其個人情況，需要照顧祖母，認為只要其人事擔保比其他被告多，同樣可獲保釋。<br />\n<br />\n法官續稱，控方稱最近潛逃案件增加，但如辯方所指，並非每人都會潛逃。他考慮各人的特別情況，最終批准四人以 10 萬元現金保釋、每周三次到警署報到、交出旅遊證件及 BNO、不得離港、遵守朝 10 晚 8 宵禁，及不得直接或間接接觸控方證人；四名被告各有 5 萬至 18 萬元的人事擔保。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，多部校內閉路電視拍攝到被告身處校園及自修室內的情況，亦有相關的學生證拍卡紀錄，控方亦有檢取被告 whatsapp 記錄、衣物等作證據。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E5%9B%9B%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%B2%E8%AC%80%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95-%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E9%80%BE%E6%9C%88%E7%B5%82%E7%8D%B2%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B-%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E6%8C%87%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E9%9C%80%E8%80%83%E8%A9%A6-%E6%93%94%E4%BF%9D%E6%A2%9D%E4%BB%B6%E5%8F%AF%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E5%259B%259B%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25B8%25B2%25E8%25AC%2580%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595-%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E9%2580%25BE%25E6%259C%2588%25E7%25B5%2582%25E7%258D%25B2%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E9%259C%2580%25E8%2580%2583%25E8%25A9%25A6-%25E6%2593%2594%25E4%25BF%259D%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E8%25A1%25A1%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E9%259A%25AA%2F&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oAz7jHi%2Fw8vyA5J9XtqU0Cw%3D&h=2a3a3c3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E5%259B%259B%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25B8%25B2%25E8%25AC%2580%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595-%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E9%2580%25BE%25E6%259C%2588%25E7%25B5%2582%25E7%258D%25B2%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E9%259C%2580%25E8%2580%2583%25E8%25A9%25A6-%25E6%2593%2594%25E4%25BF%259D%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E8%25A1%25A1%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E9%259A%25AA%2F&h=95a093fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E5%9B%9B%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%B